name: Phoebus Catastrophe
description:
It was when the darkest mist storming for decades, Sun Soldiers were hiding and frightened. Some were struggling, and some died. 

It was until the Star Summoner reached the right timing, and offered The God of Light a calamity. Phoebus Catastrophe, burning all the ashes to none.
